          <h2 class="h3">Ways of working</h2>
          <p>We help our clients identify and adopt new delivery tools and techniques, and the interlocking artefacts needed throughout product development lifecycles. We consult on, define and document delivery toolkits - and guide our clients in how to on-board new team members, develop agile mindsets and behaviours or delivery practices as they scale. Our delivery team understand the different stages of the product lifecycle and can work across all of them, establishing short feedback loops and constant improvement.</p>
        </div>
