          <h2 class="h3">Robust governance </h2>
          <p>A clear set of accurate metrics, ideally live, or regularly produced and visible to all, allows the whole team to understand how a project or product is stacking up against agreed commercial, scheduling and performance indicators. We ensure governance is robust, risks are managed, and teams are unhindered in their efforts. We provide senior coaching in the agile delivery projects and development of teams and we advise our clients on digital team shapes and structures – helping to develop skills matrices, job descriptions, and recruitment strategies.</p>
